	be used to interact for a document password. Continuations for using with
	the mentioned service are Abort and Approve.
	</P>

    @see com::sun::star::task::PasswordRequest
    @see com::sun::star::task::DocumentMSPasswordRequest
    
    @since OOo 3.3
*/
